Deprecated. 

@Deprecated
public class DynamicMarker
extends Marker

Dynamic marker on the map. This is very similar to normal marker, with the exception that this marker is always considered to be visible - thus marker is drawn immediately to screen when the view is changed. For performance reasons, if large number of markers are needed, Marker instances are preferred.
